# Grow Shell

Official name for the student dashboard aesthetic: warm cream canvas, rounded bento cards, coral serif accents, pill controls.

**Invoke in chat:** "Use Grow Shell", "Apply Grow Shell design", or "Grow Shell page"

## Quick start

```tsx
import { GrowShell, GrowHeader, grow } from "@/components/grow-shell"
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"

export default function MyPage() {
  return (
    <MainLayout>
      <GrowShell>
        <GrowHeader title="My page" accent="keep growing" description="Optional subtitle" />
        <div className="grow-toolbar">{/* search / filters */}</div>
        <div className="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <div className="grow-card-coral p-5">Stat</div>
          <div className="grow-card p-5">Stat</div>
          <div className="grow-card-dark p-5">Stat</div>
        </div>
        <div className="grow-card p-5">Content</div>
      </GrowShell>
    </MainLayout>
  )
}
```

## Class reference (`grow` from `@/lib/grow-shell`)

| Class | Use |
|-------|-----|
| `grow-shell` | Page canvas (via `<GrowShell>`) |
| `grow-bento` | Card hover grid wrapper |
| `grow-card` | Default white bento card |
| `grow-card-muted` | Warm off-white card |
| `grow-card-accent` | Lilac card |
| `grow-card-lime` | Lime peer/social card |
| `grow-card-dark` | Navy stat card |
| `grow-card-coral` | Coral gradient hero stat |
| `grow-tabs-list` + `grow-tab-trigger` | Pill tab bar |
| `grow-toolbar` | Search/filter bar |
| `grow-input` | Rounded inputs |
| `grow-btn-primary` / `grow-btn-outline` | Pill buttons |
| `grow-empty` | Dashed empty state |
| `grow-badge` | Small uppercase pill label |

## Design tokens

- Canvas: `#ffffff` · Ink: `#1c1917` · Accent: `#e85d4a` (serif italic)
- Card radius: `1.75rem` · Navy: `#1a1f2e` · Progress: `#7c6cf0`

## Rules

- **Student pages:** `<GrowShell>` inside `<MainLayout>` (or `<GrowMainLayout>`)
- **Admin & teacher pages:** use `<GrowMainLayout>` from `@/components/layouts/grow-main-layout`
- Use `<GrowHeader>` / `<PageHeader accent="…">` / `<TeacherPageHeader>` with accent for the signature title pattern
- Prefer `grow-*` classes over ad-hoc colors; match existing pages: dashboard, courses, materials, training, settings
- Course cards: `CourseCard` with `variant="bento"` (default)
- Do not apply Grow Shell to immersive learn views (`/courses/.../learn`) unless asked
